  "title": "SFFV in refinement list: when there is no result, the show more doesn't work afterwards",
  "body": "A user on our [community forum](https://discourse.algolia.com/t/show-more-option-not-working-after-facet-value-search-in-instansearch-js/3204) found a bug when using \"search for facet values\" with \"show more\".\r\n\r\nHe did a video in which he shows [how to reproduce the bug](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q5gXj-hT2ws&feature=player_embedded).\r\n\r\nSteps to reproduce the issue:\r\n - have a [refinement list with search for facet values and show more activated](https://jsfiddle.net/xe6drzyh/1/)\r\n - search until no results\r\n - remove the search\r\n - show more is not usable anymore",
